Job description
The job holder will be responsible for producing shop drawings and production setup drawings in accordance with contract and submittal requirements.
Specific tasks
Produce technical drawings (AutoCAD);
Prepare technical documents for dispatch to customers;
Produce TQCs;
Receive approved or annotated technical documents and make any necessary changes;
Prepare requisitions and purchase orders;
Execute production runs based on measurements received from the project manager;
Follow-up on standardized technical drawings from suppliers;
All other related tasks;
Desired qualifications and assets
Training in technical drawing;
Experience in the field of construction (a plus);
